:name: Mi-V
:description: This script runs Zephyr RTOS shell sample on a Mi-V RISC-V board.

$name?="Mi-V"

using sysbus
mach create $name
machine LoadPlatformDescription @platforms/cpus/miv_mixed_overlapping_memory.repl

$bin?=@https://dl.antmicro.com/projects/renode/shell-demo-miv.elf-s_803248-ea4ddb074325b2cc1aae56800d099c7cf56e592a

showAnalyzer uart

macro reset
"""
    sysbus LoadELF $bin false true cpu
"""
runMacro $reset
